</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="263" pageNumber="868" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="263.[166,1374,297,1316]" pageId="263" pageNumber="868">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[166,401,1006,1040]" pageId="263" pageNumber="868">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The North-eastern Peninsula Hill Rat is probably nocturnal and terrestrial.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[167,1107,1090,1119]" pageId="263" pageNumber="868" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="263.[166,1374,297,1316]" box="[167,1107,1090,1119]" pageId="263" pageNumber="868">
